\subtree{
\title{Example Prompts}
\subtree{
\title{Market Overview Section}
\pre{\startverb
Write a comprehensive market overview section for the [Electric Vehicle Charging Infrastructure] market. Include:
- Clear market definition and scope
- Industry ecosystem with key stakeholders
- Value chain analysis
- Historical evolution of the market
- Current market dynamics

Generate 2 supporting visuals using scientific-schematics.
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Competitive Landscape Section}
\pre{\startverb
Analyze the competitive landscape for the [Cloud Computing] market. Include:
- Porter's Five Forces analysis with High/Medium/Low ratings
- Top 10 competitors with market share
- Competitive positioning matrix
- Strategic group mapping
- Barriers to entry analysis

Generate 4 supporting visuals including Porter's Five Forces diagram and positioning matrix.
\stopverb}
}

\subtree{
\title{Strategic Recommendations Section}
\pre{\startverb
Develop strategic recommendations for entering the [Renewable Energy Storage] market. Include:
- 5-7 prioritized recommendations
- Opportunity sizing for each
- Implementation considerations
- Risk factors and mitigations
- Success criteria

Generate 3 supporting visuals including opportunity matrix and priority framework.
\stopverb}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Checklist: 50+ Page Validation}
\p{Before finalizing the report, verify:}

\subtree{
\title{Structure Completeness}
\ul{
\li{[ ] Cover page with hero visual}
\li{[ ] Table of contents (auto-generated)}
\li{[ ] List of figures (auto-generated)}
\li{[ ] List of tables (auto-generated)}
\li{[ ] Executive summary (2-3 pages)}
\li{[ ] All 11 core chapters present}
\li{[ ] Appendix A: Methodology}
\li{[ ] Appendix B: Data tables}
\li{[ ] Appendix C: Company profiles}
\li{[ ] References/Bibliography}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Visual Completeness (Core 5-6)}
\ul{
\li{[ ] Market growth trajectory chart (Priority 1)}
\li{[ ] TAM/SAM/SOM diagram (Priority 2)}
\li{[ ] Porter's Five Forces (Priority 3)}
\li{[ ] Competitive positioning matrix (Priority 4)}
\li{[ ] Risk heatmap (Priority 5)}
\li{[ ] Executive summary infographic (Priority 6, optional)}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Additional Visuals (Generate as Needed)}
\ul{
\li{[ ] Market ecosystem diagram}
\li{[ ] Regional breakdown chart}
\li{[ ] Segment growth chart}
\li{[ ] Industry trends/PESTLE diagram}
\li{[ ] Market share chart}
\li{[ ] Customer segmentation chart}
\li{[ ] Technology roadmap}
\li{[ ] Regulatory timeline}
\li{[ ] Opportunity matrix}
\li{[ ] Implementation timeline}
\li{[ ] Financial projections chart}
\li{[ ] Other section-specific visuals}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Content Quality}
\ul{
\li{[ ] All statistics have sources}
\li{[ ] Projections include assumptions}
\li{[ ] Frameworks properly applied}
\li{[ ] Recommendations are actionable}
\li{[ ] Writing is professional quality}
\li{[ ] No placeholder or incomplete sections}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Technical Quality}
\ul{
\li{[ ] PDF compiles without errors}
\li{[ ] All figures render correctly}
\li{[ ] Cross-references work}
\li{[ ] Bibliography complete}
\li{[ ] Page count exceeds 50}
}
}
}

